The adapted portions in src/data_sources/astock.py include ticker
normalisation, Tencent quote parsing, and a Sina K-line fallback. They were
modified for this project to remove TradingAgents runtime, configuration, and
agent dependencies; add a project-owned Eastmoney OHLCV primary source;
support injectable HTTP sessions and isolated caller-controlled caches; and
normalise errors and DataFrame schemas for this project's deterministic
financial-table workflow.
